{"tid":694893,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"早排放工返屋企發現我老婆同另一個男人一齊","createTime":"2018-06-08T17:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T08:07:39.000Z","uid":73202,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f279d1c8f3f8666e688d08aed9f6d32177b9312","tid":694893,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:48:44.000Z","msg":"仲記得嗰日係NBA Final...<br />\n我放工返到屋企 見到有個陌生男人同我老婆坐喺廳<br />\n個男人見到我呆咗一呆 就話自己係上嚟睇NBA Final <br />\n(自稱我老婆嘅朋友)，話自己支持騎士<br />\n我屌你老母 真係當我三歲細佬呀？<br />\n老實講 嗰陣我真係好嬲 仲要講大話呃鳩我？<br />\n睇你個樣就知你係支持勇士㗎啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d2bc2f6e6dac61ac2fdb910e8e13a83a3a9e6f","tid":694893,"uid":119511,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:52:12.000Z","msg":"兩隊佢都撐<br />\n上去你屋企騎你老婆仲唔係騎士加勇士？"},{"pid":"e1a9202727b5d7dabcc01e65139e7154af41a680","tid":694893,"uid":154419,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/09/020053_a0a93d083ebd57166c9f4fb3a8ec2021.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F09%2F020053_a0a93d083ebd57166c9f4fb3a8ec2021.png&h=ea6f0ea6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63b0bd1397d9423129f4f4f5d5f29d4ca671d338","tid":694893,"uid":179589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:08:00.000Z","msg":"我係咪錯重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75f571641f891ddf641270c5e97e142a8da483e","tid":694893,"uid":118217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1a9202727b5d7dabcc01e65139e7154af41a680","tid":694893,"uid":154419,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/09/020053_a0a93d083ebd57166c9f4fb3a8ec2021.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F20